column4: NSLOCTEXT("[CF564B79411EA6E908F95DB86BC784EB]", "EABBD51C4073D5612F2ED492ACEC7B72", "Wow it stinks! Is this a Trash Pile?")
NSLOCTEXT("[CF564B79411EA6E908F95DB86BC784EB]", "4127799E410A8964FB792B8798975E5A", "I didn\'t know there\'s one in Digimon World.")
NSLOCTEXT("[CF564B79411EA6E908F95DB86BC784EB]", "F74A4F2B46F04D26115477BCEC8D602E", "Wow, this is interesting! I\'ve never seen anything like this!")
NSLOCTEXT("[CF564B79411EA6E908F95DB86BC784EB]", "CFCAB7134EBCB8955D5322A6C30AE830", "Oh my goodness! The poop are moving and talking!")
NSLOCTEXT("[CF564B79411EA6E908F95DB86BC784EB]", "0D8D4B164E80756C419DD897AE503E77", "Are you talking about me? I\'m Sukamon... I\'m a Mutant Digimon.")
NSLOCTEXT("[CF564B79411EA6E908F95DB86BC784EB]", "D57627C3471A8EA182D3979889E52741", "In a way, you are right, cuz we are made from Digital Waste.")
NSLOCTEXT("[CF564B79411EA6E908F95DB86BC784EB]", "91DD55754B3B3EF5C5EC5BA4B8272F4C", "Should we ask him to come to the city, too? We shouldn\'t be prejudiced.")
NSLOCTEXT("[CF564B79411EA6E908F95DB86BC784EB]", "BEB523B3430E0E54B662D792427416F7", "Well, this is a paradise only for the Sukamon Tribe. Others can\'t live here.")
NSLOCTEXT("[CF564B79411EA6E908F95DB86BC784EB]", "7AEC12C74DD18463F6814E97802268DE", "Then you can\'t live in other places?")
NSLOCTEXT("[CF564B79411EA6E908F95DB86BC784EB]", "19BA4FF54AE3B01AF741859966754AE8", "Of course not! What do you think?")
NSLOCTEXT("[CF564B79411EA6E908F95DB86BC784EB]", "9347676A48EAF62BD67D82869242A956", "Well, although you can\'t live here, you can look around.")
NSLOCTEXT("[CF564B79411EA6E908F95DB86BC784EB]", "D66E8976411CEF66B3D7078DDD115DA2", "Oh, by the way, don\'t ever make the King mad.")
NSLOCTEXT("[CF564B79411EA6E908F95DB86BC784EB]", "570710DF4809B36EA8D011822D9BB09A", "You\'ll be turned into something miserable by the King\'s Digivolve technique.")
